descriptionHtml:
This is an alternate race for Khajiit, a human form, for people who do not like playing animals as characters.
This has the same exact stats of the original Khajiit, the only difference is the look!

Disclaimer: Any mods that are shown in my pictures are purely cosmetic and are not apart of the mod itself. I claim no ownership to any mods visible within my images that are showing the race only. Mods represented within the images are the property of said mods
